---
/**
 * ProblemSection.astro
 * Highlights customer pain points and creates urgency
 */
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">
        When Your Furnace Fails, <span class="text-red-600">Every Minute Matters</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Michigan winters don't wait. Neither should you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Problem Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <!-- Problem 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-red-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">No Heat Emergency</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          It's 10°F outside and your furnace just quit. Your family is freezing, and you need help <strong>now</strong> — not tomorrow.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-yellow-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-orange-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 9.293 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Can't Trust "Cheap" Fixes</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          You've been burned by unlicensed handymen before. Band-aid repairs that fail again in weeks. You need <strong>real experts</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-red-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-yellow-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-yellow-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M8.433 7.418c.155-.103.346-.196.567-.267v1.698a2.305 2.305 0 01-.567-.267C8.07 8.34 8 8.114 8 8c0-.114.07-.34.433-.582zM11 12.849v-1.698c.22.071.412.164.567.267.364.243.433.468.433.582 0 .114-.07.34-.433.582a2.305 2.305 0 01-.567.267z"/>
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-13a1 1 0 10-2 0v.092a4.535 4.535 0 00-1.676.662C6.602 6.234 6 7.009 6 8c0 .99.602 1.765 1.324 2.246.48.32 1.054.545 1.676.662v1.941c-.391-.127-.68-.317-.843-.504a1 1 0 10-1.51 1.31c.562.649 1.413 1.076 2.353 1.253V15a1 1 0 102 0v-.092a4.535 4.535 0 001.676-.662C13.398 13.766 14 12.991 14 12c0-.99-.602-1.765-1.324-2.246A4.535 4.535 0 0011 9.092V7.151c.391.127.68.317.843.504a1 1 0 101.511-1.31c-.563-.649-1.413-1.076-2.354-1.253V5z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Afraid of Being Overcharged</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Hidden fees, surprise charges, pressure tactics. You want <strong>transparent pricing</strong> and honest recommendations.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Call-out Box -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-red-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center text-white">
      <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        You Deserve Better Than "Good Enough"
      </h3>
      <p class="text-xl text-red-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Licensed Michigan HVAC experts who show up fast, fix it right the first time, and give you upfront pricing. No games. No surprises.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/home-visit" class="bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors">
          Get Expert Help Now
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+18334948669" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          Call (833) FIX-IT-NOW
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
